records.name: Machchafushi Island Resort & Spa Maldives, The Centara Collection

descriptions.direction: Located in Machchafushi, Machchafushi Island Resort & Spa Maldives, The Centara Collection is on a private beach. Maafushivaru Island Jetty and Villingilivaru Island Pier are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Maafushivaru Island Beach and Vakarufalhi Island Beach. Dhangethi Beach and Ranveli Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. Looking to get your feet wet? Scuba diving, windsurfing and swimming adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Property Location When you stay at Machchafushi Island Resort & Spa Maldives, The Centara Collection in Machchafushi, you'll be within a 5-minute walk of Dhangethi Beach. This beach resort is within close proximity of Maafushivaru Island Jetty and Maafushivaru Island Beach.Rooms Make yourself at home in one of the 112 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and minibars (stocked with some free items). Rooms have private balconies or patios. Flat-screen televisions with cable programming provide entertainment, while complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected. Bathrooms feature bathtubs or showers, complimentary toiletries, and hair dryers.Dining All-inclusive rates are available at this resort. Meals and beverages at onsite dining establishments are included in all-inclusive rates. Charges may be applied for dining at some restaurants, special dinners and dishes, some beverages, and other amenities. Enjoy international cuisine at Reef Restaurant, one of the resort's 3 restaurants, or stay in and take advantage of the 24-hour room service. Snacks are also available at the coffee shop/cafe. Relax with a refreshing drink from the poolside bar or one of the 2 bars/lounges. Rec, Spa, Premium Amenities Pamper yourself with a visit to the spa, which offers massages, body treatments, and facials. After dipping into one of the 2 outdoor swimming pools, you can spend some time at the private beach. Additional amenities at this resort include concierge services, an arcade/game room, and wedding services.Business, Other Amenities Featured amenities include complimentary newspapers in the lobby, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. heck-out time ends at12:00|Check-in time ends at00:00|Check-in time starts at15:00|Minimum check-in age is18|Special check-in instructions Guests must transfer via Airplane to the property. Guests must contact the property at least 72 hours before travel, using the contact information on the confirmation received after booking. Front desk staff will greet guests on arrival. At check-in, guests must provide either a negative PCR COVID-19 test result or a record of full COVID-19 vaccination. Guests providing a negative COVID-19 test result must have been tested no more than 48 hours prior to check-in. For more details, please contact the property using the information on the booking confirmation. Guests must arrange transfers (surcharge) from Male International Airport to the property, which is 25 minutes away via seaplane. To guarantee transfers, guests must contact the property with their flight details at least 4 days before their expected arrival. Daily transfer service is offered between 6 AM and 3:45 PM. Guests arriving or departing outside of these hours are advised to book a local hotel room in Male or Hulhumale. Luggage in excess of 20 kg/person may incur a fee, payable to the seaplane company during flight check-in. Guests must pay the seaplane transfer fee at check-out. Guests must arrange transfers (surcharge) from Male International Airport to the property, which is 30 minutes away via domestic flight, followed by a speedboat transfer to the property. To guarantee transfers, guests must contact the property with their flight details at least 4 days before their expected arrival. Daily transfer service is offered by Maldivian Airways/FlyMe before 10:30 PM. Guests arriving outside of these hours are advised to book a hotel room in Male or Hulhumale until services resume. Guests must pay the domestic flight fee and the speedboat fee at check-out. The additional fee (payable at the property) covers transfer fees for guests ages 12-17.Know Before You Go Pool access available from 8:00 AM to 7:00 PM.Reservations are required for massage services and spa treatments. Reservations can be made by contacting the resort prior to arrival, using the contact information on the booking confirmation.No pets and no service animals are allowed at this property.Set meals are served in guestrooms only (no menus or public dining).This property advises that enhanced cleaning and guest safety measures are currently in place.Disinfectant is used to clean the property.Personal protective equipment, including masks, will be available to guests.Social distancing measures are in place; staff at the property wear personal protective equipment; a shield is in place between staff and guests in main contact areas; guests are provided with hand sanitizer.Contactless check-out is available.Individually-wrapped food options are available for breakfast, lunch, and dinner, and also through room service.Each guestroom is kept vacant for a minimum of 72 hours between bookings.At check-in, guests must provide either a negative PCR COVID-19 test result or a record of full COVID-19 vaccination.Guest providing a negative COVID-19 test result must have been tested no more than 48 hours prior to check-in. Mandatory Fees and TaxesYou'll be asked to pay the following charges at the property: CHRISTMAS GALA DINNER AS PER MEAL PLANBed & Breakfast – Adult - USD 340 net and Children (6 -11.99 yrs)- USD 170 netOther Meal plan (Half Board/Full Board/All-Inclusive/Grand All-Inclusive) – Adult - USD 260 net and Children (6 -11.99 yrs) - USD 130 netNEW YEAR GALA DINNER AS PER MEAL PLANBed & Breakfast – Adult - USD 380 net and Children (6 -11.99 yrs)- USD 190 netOther Meal plan (Half Board/Full Board/All-Inclusive/Grand All-Inclusive) – Adult - USD 310 net and Children (6 -11.99 yrs)- USD 155 netWe have included all charges provided to us by the property.The additional fee covers transfer fees for guests ages 12-17. FeesRollaway bed fee: USD 200.0 per nightThe above list may not be comprehensive. Fees and deposits may not include tax and are subject to change. Peak period: 24 Dec 2024 – 7 Jan 2025Cancellation policy:Cancel less than 30 day(s) before check in, charge 100% of total stay, No-show charge 100%. (apply all rate plans)Payment – 100% at the time of making a bookingNo check out/ No departure on 31 Dec 2024|Green Tax (Property Collect): Increase from USD 6 to USD 12 per person per night for stay periods beginning January 1, 2025 onward. Children under 2 years are exempt from this Green Tax under the updated regulation.|Please note, some room types at this property are not available when booking a stay with children.|No elevators|No rollaway/extra beds available|No pets or service animals allowed|Pets not allowed
